\\ E.g.f.: 1024/3125 * exp(5*x) - 81*(1+4*x)/256 * exp(4*x) + 4*x*(2+3*x)/9 * exp(3*x) - x^2*(3+2*x)/6 * exp(2*x) - 81171/7200000 + 713*x/180000 - 9*x^2/4000 + x^3/150 + x^4/120.
